==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cairngormstone
<hw>Cairn*gorm"stone`</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>.
<ety>[Gael. <ets>carn</ets> a cairn + <ets>gorm</ets> azure.]</ety>
<fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A smoky yellow or brown variety of rock crystal,
or crystallized quartz, found especially, in the mountain of
<etsep>Cairngorm</etsep>, in Scotland.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> smoky quartz.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

